Rajiv Gandhi (20 Agostt 1944 - 20 May 1991) ho Bhartacho satvo prodhanmontri aslolo. Indira Gandhi ani Firoz Gandhi hancho,  to vhoddlo put. To Nehru ghoranneatlo tisro prodhan montri aslolo.  Indira Gandhichea mornna uprant,  31 okttobr 1984 te 2 disembr 1989 meren to Bhartache prodhanomontri aslolo. Jedna Rajiv Gandhin prodhanmontri podachi sutram jedna hatant ghetli tedna te bhartache tornnatte prodhanomontri aslole. Tea vellar taji  pirai fokot 40 vorsam aslolim. 
Rajiv Gandhi rajkaronnant eunche adim Indeiche Airlinant voimanik aslolo. Tachi Avoi Indira Gandhi zori Bhartacheo prodhanmontri asloli tori astona to rajkaronnatlean pois raup posont kelolem. Mojgotim, Inglonddatlea Kambridge videapitthant xikot astana tanchi vollokh Ittaliyon vonxachea Sonia kodden zali ani magir tanche logn zale. Uprant 1980 tazo  bhav Sanjay Gandhi hanchea mornna uprant mat tannem  rajkaronnant provex kelo. Mukhar tanchi Avoi  Indira Gandhi hanchea hotea zalea uprant 1984 te Bhartache prodhanmontri zale. 
Rajiv Gandhichea fuddar ponnakhala kongresin tache uprant zalolea loksobha venchnnukent 542 poiki 411 suvatancher zoit melloilem. Rajiv Gandhichea adhunik vicharancho pogddo tanchea sudharonnavadi kamantlean pollounk mell'llo. Tennem  Bhartak songnnok yugachi vollokh korun dili. Toxench tanchea dhornnantleanuch telikomachi survat zali. 
1988t tanem  Xrilonkent xantisena dhaddpacho nirnnoi ghetlo. Tachi porinniti LTTE vangdda zal'lea songhrxant zali. Heach kallant tancher zal'lea bofors ghottallean zal'lea aropamni tanchea nitoll rajkaronnachi protima mhelli zali. Nimanne, 1989 loksobha venchnnukent tanka opes aile. 
Tache uprantuy te kongres pokxache odhyokx aslole. Tanchea uprant tanchi ghorkan'n Sonia Gandhi, tancho cholo Rahul Gandhi ani choli Priyanka Gandhi rajkaronnat ailim. 
Rajiv Gandhik mornnauporant Bharat Ratna puraskar dilo. 

====Surveche jivit====

rajivo gandhicho zolm' bhartatlea famad rajki-i ghorannean zalo. Tancho azo zovahorolal nehru bharti-i suttke zhunzatole mukhel fuddari ani bhartache poile prodhanomontri axil'le. Zovahorolal nehru hanchi choli indira gandhi hinnem kangresiche ek vangddi firoz gandhi (he dhorman parxi axil'le) hanche vangdda logn kele. Indira gandhin i.So. 1944t rajivo gandhik zolm' dilo. Ya kallan tanche auy bapuy svotontr loddheat vanttekar zal'lean sodanch kadyent astalem. Nimannem i.So. 1947t svatontry mell'llea uprant te olahabad sthayik zale. Punn i.So. 1949chea sumarak indira ani firoz hanchemodim (durava) nirmann zala. Ani indira bhurgeamsoit bapaikodden dil'lik aileo ani mukhar bapaivangoddach rauli.I.So. 1960t firoz gandhi kallzachea atakan bhair poddle.

====Xikxonn ani voivahik jivit====

rajivo gandhichem surveche xikop bordding skulat zalem. 1961n mukhavelea xikxonnakhatir te londdnak gelem. Kembrizak astona 1965chea zanevarin tanchi vollokh ittlichea ॲnttoniya maino(Antonia Maino- sonia gandhi) hichekodden zali. Mukhar 1968t tamnni bhartan yeun logn kelem. 1967t auy indira gandhi bhartacheo prodhanomontri zaleo tori rajivo rajkaronnapasun pois ravun inddiyon eorolainsat voimanik mhonn kam' pollounk lagle. Tankam 1970t rahul zalear 1972t prianka hi don bhurgim zalim.

====Rajkaronnan provex====

1980t lhan bhavo sonzoi gandhi rajkaronnan kam' kortalo tacho viman opghatan moronn zalem. Hachea uprant auy ani kangres pokx hanchekoddlean rajivo gandhicher rajkaronnan yeupakhatir dobavo yeunk laglo. Rajivo ani sonia dogamycho rajkaronnant yeupak virodh axil'loch. Toxi zahir voktovea rajivan kel'li. Tori mukhar vichar bodlun 1981t tamnni ometthisaun loksobha venchnnuk loddhoili. Tamnni lokdolachem umedovar xorod yadou hancho 2 lakh motamni porabhou kelo. Beginuch te aiche mukhel sol'lagar toxench yuvk kangresichem mukheli zalem.
Prodhanomontripod

31 ekttobor 1984 disa indirajinchim hotea zali. Rajivo gandhicher prodhanomontri podachi zobabodari sopoili. Indirajinchim hotea zaleauporant dil'lit xikhanchea virodhat zaleo. Sumar 2700 xikh hatunt melem. Heavixim kangres fuddareancher dongli korpache aropuy zale. Hea vixim dil'lit eka suvalleat rajivo gandhin kaddil'le udgar mukhavelea promann. “Some riots took place in the country following the murder of Indiraji. We know the people were very angry and for a few days it seemed that India had been shaken. But, when a mighty tree falls, it is only natural that the earth around it does shake a little.” jen'na vhodd rukh poddtta ten'na sorbhomvotonnochi zomin halta ani te sahjikuch asa. Ya vyoktoveavoilean rajivo gandhicher khub ttika zali. Prodhanomontri podacher venchnnuk zaleauporant rajivo gandhin loksobha borkhast korit venchnnuko ghetleo. Khub motamni kangres venchun aili. Tanchea svochchh protimecho tankam faido zaloch. Tamnni roxia vangddoche ixttagotichem sombondh chodd ghott'tt kelem toxench omerikechi somyukt somsthana ani chin hanche vangdda borem sombond douropachem yotn kelem.

==Orthik dhornnam==

rajivo gandhin tontrogoneana sombondan axil'lea ayaticher sutt dili.Khas korun songnnok, dursonchar mollar tamnni khaxelem yotn kelem. Lains raz sopoupacho yotn korit tamnni ayatichem niym' komi kelem.

====Hotea====

1991t loksobha venchnnukanchea procharosobhe mojgotim litt'tte hamnni manvi bombacho vapor korun rajivo gandhichi hotea keli. “dhonu” namvanchi choli rajivo gandhichea sobhasthollakodde zomil'lea gordent axil'li. Rajivo gandhi lagim yetach ti gordentlean mukhar yeupacho yotn ti korunk lagli. Ten'na rajivo gandhichea bail surkxarokxokan tika addailem. Punn rajivo gandhin te bail rokxikek thamboun dhonuk lagim yeupachi porvanogi dili. Dhonu rajivo gandhichea paya poddpak bagouli ani tinnem aplea komrek axil'li sfottkacho sfott kelo. Hatunt ticho, rajivo gandhi ani lagim ubem axil'lem monis melem. Litt'tten survek zobabodari gheupachem nhoikaril'lem punn ghoddnnuk thollachem chitrikoronn upolbd zalea uprant, her dohxotovadeanchi vollokh pottoun sod ghetlo. Haka lagun litt'tten bhartachi uril'li suril'li sohanobhuti tor soplich te vangddach litt'ttek dohxotovadi songhttona mhonn tharaupi bharot ho poilo des tharlo. Hache onukoronn korit 32 dexamni litt'ttek dohxotovadi ghoxit kelem.
